    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six engine. This high-revving powerplant features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, both of which have been recently serviced for optimal timing and compression. Power is sent through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement plates to mitigate common fatigue points, and the suspension retains its communicative MacPherson strut and multi-link geometry. While the exterior shows minor signs of road use, the drivetrain is robust, providing the tactile feedback and 8,000 RPM redline performance these icons are known for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
