    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a refined driving experience and the peace of mind that comes from consistent, high-quality care. The exterior is finished in a timeless metallic finish that still holds a deep, impressive luster. While there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use, the body is straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, smoke-free environment. The premium leather upholstery has been regularly conditioned and shows only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, with all stitching intact. Every technological feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the responsive infotainment system\u2014works exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs whisper-quiet. I have kept a comprehensive folder of all service records, including a recent major interval service that involved a fresh synthetic oil change, new filters, and a full brake pad replacement. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, ensuring you won't face immediate maintenance costs. This is a reliable, turn-key car for someone who appreciates mechanical integrity and a well-preserved interior.",
